   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educate a Girl Child, Empower a Nation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Despite India&apos;s push to guarantee education to all children (RtE Act, 2009) only 33% of girls complete Class XII (Ministry of HRD). Education is one of the key areas for girls/ women empowerment. We, at VRDS, have been promoting girls&apos; education, to prevent child labour, child marriage and other abuses, and promote gender equality as part of our holistic effort towards community development in Haveri district of Karnataka. We seek your support to educate 100+ girl children through our project.</narrative>
  </description>
